      <div>
        <p><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="address"><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="intitulatio">M . Rex Scott’</seg> . Priori de Goldingham <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="salutation">salutem</seg> .</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="disposition"><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="notification">Sciatis quod</seg> uolo et firmiter precipio ut<lb/> plenarie habeatis omnem libertatem quam uobis priori carta mea confirmaui
                     scilicet . ut habe<lb/>atis bosca uestra et Garenniam uestram per terram uestram et ut de Boscis
                     uestris aut de Ga<lb/>rennia uestra nullus intromittere . uel in illis quicumque capere presumat nisi
                     per uos . et siquis forte hanc<lb/> uestram libertatem infringere presumpserit  super meam plenariam forisfacturam
                     hoc faciet .</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="witnesses">t<ex>estibus</ex> Waltero<lb/> cancellario . D<ex>aui</ex>d olifard .</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="dating">apud Castell<ex>um</ex> puellar<ex>um</ex> .</seg></p>
